<h3>Startup Leadership Program <small>Shanghai-based Startup Network</small></h3>
<p><img src="/img/startupleadershipprogram.png" alt="Startup Leadership Program"></p><p>The Startup Leadership Program (SLP) is a highly selective, 80-hour, 6-month world-class training program and lifetime network for outstanding founders and innovators. SLP Fellows have founded 700 companies that have raised $370 million, and include breakthrough and award-winning startups like Savored, TomNod, Ixigo, NatureBox, SideTour, Micello, Momelan, Novira, Runkeeper, Sensobi, Shareaholic, Solar Junction, Voicetap and Ubersense.</p>
